{"word":"καταφράζω","slug":"καταφράζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταφράζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><i>to declare</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, with aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> and <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a>, <i>to consider, think upon, ponder</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>; <el>καταφρασθείς</el> <i>observed</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}